23:37.186 --> 23:46.738
and you guys are young, you're able to keep up with the pace, and you often live very full and rushed lives, and you come to the Bible, and there's a normal kind of pace of life.

23:47.399 --> 23:54.808
There's a pace at which you read these screens, and the screens teach you, the pixels teach you, this F pattern of reading through how you can scan.

23:54.848 --> 23:57.070
