24:01.336 --> 24:06.482
This book rewards a slow, unhurried reading.

24:07.874 --> 24:16.605
When they wrote this book, there was no internet, no keyboards, not like people just punch out some keys and publish it on the worldwide web.

24:17.706 --> 24:19.869
