25:16.029 --> 25:27.647
Christian meditation means filling your mind with God's word and then lingering there, chewing on it, mulling it over, letting it go around a little bit.

25:27.667 --> 25:34.578
It's like you put something on your palate and instead of swallowing it immediately, you enjoy the taste and keep it in your mouth.

25:34.786 --> 25:35.447
for a little bit.

25:35.467 --> 25:36.568
So meditation is doing.

25:37.109 --> 25:39.992
It's pausing to linger over what you've read.

25:41.093 --> 25:48.080
I told you, you can read faithfully, productively in just a few minutes of God's Word.

25:48.281 --> 25:53.506
Chlorious, amazing truths that are way too precious and sweet to just read and then move on.

25:56.289 --> 25:58.392
You need to linger a little bit over it.

25:59.032 --> 26:00.274
Give it some time.

26:00.334 --> 26:01.495
Try to enjoy it.

26:02.116 --> 26:02.716
Chew on it.

26:02.837 --> 26:04.178
Enjoy the juices.

26:04.802 --> 26:14.132
