26:26.524 --> 26:32.050
His word is not just going in your ear and out the other, but it's been going, beginning to go down in your heart.

26:32.482 --> 26:36.267
so that you feel the significance of his word.

26:36.287 --> 26:37.569
It's one thing to run it through the mind.

26:37.629 --> 26:42.395
It's nothing to run it down into the heart and then to be able to respond to him in prayer.

26:42.415 --> 26:49.845
That's where communion with God happens when we linger in his word in meditation and then respond to him in prayer.

26:50.546 --> 26:52.809
The meditation's the Old Testament word for it.

